      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional motorcar in pristine, showroom-grade condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, exhibiting an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Performance is absolute, reflecting a history of rigorous maintenance and careful ownership. We invite the discerning collector to experience a standard of excellence rarely available on the secondary market.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
